						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="bold">Śaka 1456 (1535 A.D.)</hi></p>						

						<p>Damaged. Seems to record a gift of money by Lakkaya-Nāyakkar for some specified offerings on the occasion of the deities' halt at garden (<hi rend="italic">tōppu</hi>) of the donor. The details of the date viz., <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1456, Jaya, Makara ba. 1 Wednesday, Maghā correspond to 1535 A.D., January 20, ·38, f.d.n. ·01.</hi></p>						

